              <span id="reviewTextContainer679619536" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7830744797816660535">It amazes me the atrocities that occurred during the holocaust. This is the second book From Roberta Kagan that I have read and again I am astounded at how well written her novels are. If you have been searching for an author that writes a great historical fiction book about the holocaust then you have found her! This particular book had a happy ending along with a few heartaches as well. Overall a thoroughly enjoyable read.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


