<span id="freeTextContainer8044703862828112029">I got this as a free download from BookBub and wish I hadn&apos;t wasted my time. If you are going to mine the deplorable horror of The Holocaust for a novel, at least write a good book. The characters in this one all sound the same. They talk incessantly. They recount information in lengthy expositions of which the reader is already aware. The &quot;heroine&quot; is a shallow floozy. The villains are stock Nazis from any pulp fiction. Move along. There&apos;s nothing good here to read.</span>
