              <span id="reviewTextContainer1530314714" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4645668830083745070">This is a light read principally about a girl who has babies with every man she meets. Of course she falls deeply in love and cannot help herself. It is described as a Holocaust novel but this is a bit of an over claim. The war is going on but most of the time it barely touches the protagonists. In the last quarter it becomes more real but, in my opinion, is still pretty superficial.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


