    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2319307247" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9976871728265059533">Ms. Kagan did a wonderful job learning about the events of WWII and bringing them to life. She did a great job of integrating the events of the years with personal stories that you could easily relate to and see the war through their eyes.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

