<li class='cover' id='bookCover_58817832'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/58817832-lilia"><img alt="Lilia: a true story of love, courage, and survival in the shadow of war" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1629488518l/58817832._SX98_.jpg" />
