<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer5108043797478138956">I’m an American writer of Jewish and Romany decent. I write Historical Fiction and Historical Romance, most of which is set during the holocaust. Although I never discount the horrors of the time period, the main focus of my work is on ordinary people who prove to be strong heroic characters in unfathomable circumstances.<br/><br/>Facebook Author page:<br/><a target='_blank' rel='noopener nofollow' href='http://www.facebook.com/Rkagan4'>http://www.facebook.com/Rkagan4</a><br/><br/>Facebook Book Club:<br/><a target='_blank' rel='noopener nofollow' href='https://www.facebook.com/groups/1494285400798292/'>https:</a></span>
  <span id="freeText5108043797478138956" style="display:none">I’m an American writer of Jewish and Romany decent. I write Historical Fiction and Historical Romance, most of which is set during the holocaust. Although I never discount the horrors of the time period, the main focus of my work is on ordinary people who prove to be strong heroic characters in unfathomable circumstances.<br /><br />Facebook Author page:<br /><a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" href="http://www.facebook.com/Rkagan4">http://www.facebook.com/Rkagan4</a><br /><br />Facebook Book Club:<br /><a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/1494285400798292/">https://www.facebook.com/groups/14942...</a><br /><br />Instagram:<br />RobertaKaganAuthor</span>
